title: Frank Lloyd Wright Glass Panel—Wisteria Stained
description:
Inspired by the Frank Lloyd Wright® (American, 1867-1959) designed fireplace in the Darwin D. Martin House in Buffalo, New York, this panel conjures up emotions of fall.   Made in the USA.  The glass panel is framed with metal and comes with both a hanging chain and a display base. 

11 1/2 x 11 x 3/4 in.

 

Additional Shipping $15 per Order.

This item cannot be shipped to a destination outside the United States.
